parameters:
Ah, what should I do about the magic research
presentation?
Is the manuscript still not finished?
It's normal, right? Hiyo is just too fast.
I've been preparing for it for a while now.
Amelia just enrolled, so she's exempted, right?
If you're free, can you help me, Elena?
Isn't this something I should do myself?

Shut up. Since giving a good presentation is
beneficial for us witches, we should all
cooperate.

Magic is something that demons use, but there are
also many good magic spells.

I want magic users to be recognized and able to
live a normal life.
I dropped the fork. I'll go get a new one.
I also want some water, so I'll go with you.
[School Lunch Cook] Phew, time for a break.

[Professor Hoffman] Don't let your guard down. The
magic research presentation is coming up soon, you
know.
MasamuneI have no business with you.

[Hiyo] If you have any troubles, please feel free
to consult with me.

ElenaI thought healing magic wasn't cool, so I
kept it hidden, but it's actually a great magic.

ElenaBecoming a military doctor in the future
might be a good idea.

LeonIf I keep researching only erotic magic,
I'll get scolded by Professor Melissa. I need to
be a bit more serious in my research.

TommyFrom now on, I'll be able to do plenty of
research on my beloved grimoires. I'm looking
forward to it.

Skeleton HeadHey, my junior suddenly asked me
out for a meal, but I don't know what to talk
about.

OliviaThe punishment for the Magic Research Club
is too lenient...

OliviaWell, to be honest, there is a part of me
that feels relieved.

JacksonDamn, it's hard to eat with my injured
arm.

3rd Year SenpaiThat's right! Olivia should feed
him.

3rd Year SenpaiBut you two are interested in
each other, yet there hasn't been much progress.

3rd Year SenpaiLet's deepen your relationship on
this occasion.
OliviaIt's not like I'm interested or anything.

3rd Year SenpaiOh my, you're not being honest,
huh?

ChloeIf you want a magical tool, please let me
know anytime. But Tommy senpai's request takes top
priority.
SylvesterUm, um... What are your hobbies?

Fabia TesseriniIn this abyssal state... I will
definitely expose the secret.
Would you like to proceed with the story?

This child is a newcomer. They're still an
apprentice, you know.
And it seems like they have no memory.

When I woke up, I was in front of the academy, but
I don't remember anything before that...

Since I have nowhere else to go and it would be
difficult to return to town in the remote area,
I've decided to work here as a live-in employee.
No, just being able to survive is enough.
I look forward to working with you from now on.
You seem close, are you two dating?
I've been sneakily watching both of you.

It's not embarrassing, because you two look really
good together.

We don't really need to go around announcing that
we're dating.
I won't let anyone take you away anymore.

Professor MelissaWe need to strengthen our
vigilance for the Magic Research Presentation. We
should also ask Freya for help.
